heading: Haunted Refuge Dungeon Guide
content: Haunted Refuge features a straightforward layout, and does not contain any dangerous monsters. It is decent for farming, but is not currently a possible . There is no boss; once you slay all enemies in the Befouled Quagmire, the dungeon is complete. This dungeon unlocks the , an offensive aspect for the Barbarian. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
